text:
Mano, the outfit you were expecting has arrived.
Would you like to try it on?
Um, may I really try it on...?

Of course!
This outfit is for you, Mano.

...Th-Thank you very much...
Then, I'll go change.

Oh, Mano, it looks great on you!
You're sparkling!

Wow... Th-Thank you so much...
Um, well, the outfit is just so lovely...

It feels kind of strange...
like I've grown wings, all fluffy...

I see... yeah.
Outfits might just be the wings for idols to soar.
